---
title: Moroccan Prawns and Roast Veg Couscous with parsley yoghurt sauce
description: Perfectly pink prawns are coated with a special blend of Middle Eastern spices and drizzled with a cooling, herby yoghurt sauce in this hearty recipe that's exotic and familiar all at once.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R15_W31_IE_IEXQS25187-2_Main_high-33fb9fb8.jpg
